e=Shooting Fish|publisher=[[Cineplex Entertainment]]|accessdate=18 May 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624103746/http://www.cineplex.com/Movie/shooting-fish|archive-date=24 June 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1999\n| [[London Critics Circle]]\n| [[London Film Critics Circle Awards 1998#British Supporting Actress of the Year|British Supporting Actress of the Year]] <small>(tied with [[Minnie Driver]])</small>\n| ''The Last Days of Disco''\n| {{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2W2QCwAAQBAJ&pg=PP7&lpg=PP7&dq=kate+beckinsale+london+critics+circle+last+days+of+disco&source=bl&ots=tPkAiC7kiS&sig=JaWW1wVOqL8ewNk46wQ6Z6qAFlA&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiv1cSGw-PMAhXJrY8KHbJ9BmMQ6AEIOTAG#v=onepage&q=kate%20beckinsale%20london%20critics%20circle%20last%20days%20of%20disco&f=false|title=Celebrity Biographies \u2013 The Amazing Life Of Kate Beckinsale|last=Green|first=Matt|publisher=Matt Green}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2002\n| [[MTV Movie Awards]]\n| [[MTV Movie Award for Best Performance|Best Performance - Female]]\n| ''Pearl Harbor''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Saturn Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Saturn Award for Best Actress#2000s|Best Actress]]\n| ''Serendipity''\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"china\">{{cite news|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/showbiz/2009-11/04/content_8913819.htm|title=Kate Beckinsale|work=[[China Daily]]|date=4 November 2009|accessdate=18 May 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610104321/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/showbiz/2009-11/04/content_8913819.htm|archive-date=10 June 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''Underworld''\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"china\"/>\n|-\n| 2005\n| [[Screen Actors Guild]]\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture#2000s|Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture]] (shared with rest of cast)\n| ''The Aviator''\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref name=\"china\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2006\n| [[MTV Movie Awards]]\n